    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just never stops. the burning in my legs, the nerve pain... it's like every second is just another heavy weight i have to carry. i'm so tired of fighting a body that's constantly trying to hurt me. sometimes i just stare at the wall and think how much easier it would be if everything was just... still. forever.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
