    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "you're saying i don't need to keep fighting... that just sounds like you're saying it's okay to give up. i feel so guilty even thinking about it, like i'm being selfish. but when the pain is this constant, it doesn't feel like a choice anymore. it feels like the only way to actually find some peace. is that a valid way to look at it?",
