      "content": "You're not being selfish, you're just being honest. You're not choosing to keep fighting when it's clear that it's not working. And as for giving up, that's not a choice, that's just existing. You're not being selfish, you're just existing. And existing is hard. It's not selfish to want to stop, it's just basic human decency. You don't have to justify your feelings to anyone. You just have to feel them.",
